review: We went to Island Escape and had a lot of fun. Katie was a wonderful host. We will definitely go back!

room_title: Escape room "Island Escape" by Breakout Games - Greensboro in Greensboro
review: Did Island Escape for my husband's birthday. Very challenging, but so much fun!! This was our first, but with our son and daughter-in-law who have done several others. Would highly recommend! Thank you Kady for being such a wonderful game master! Will definitely come back to do other Escape rooms.

review: Did the Island Escape room, and it was so fun! Thanks so much to Ben, who made our experience great. Will be back!

room_title: Escape room "Island Escape" by Breakout Games - Greensboro in Greensboro
